@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Wardrobe";
}
<h2>@ViewBag.Title.</h2>
<h3>@ViewBag.Message</h3>

<div class="row">

    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>@Html.ActionLink("Headwear", "Index", "Hats")</h2>
        <p>
            From wigs, to hair clips, to hats, if something goes on the head, we recommend you place it here!
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>@Html.ActionLink("Tops", "Index", "Tops")</h2>
        <p>
            All varieties of shirts, jackets, and vests qualify!
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>@Html.ActionLink("Dresses", "Index", "Dresses")</h2>
        <p>
            Who wants to put a dress, robe, or kimono in the "tops" category?  "Not I" you say?  We've created this category just
            for people like you! 
        </p>
    </div>
</div>


<div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-4 col-md-4">
        <h2>@Html.ActionLink("Bottoms", "Index", "Bottoms")</h2>
        <p>
            The perfect place for your pants, jeans, leggings, tights, skirts, skorts, shorts, and capris!
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-sm-4 col-md-4">
        <h2>@Html.ActionLink("Shoes", "Index", "Shoes")</h2>
        <p>
            Unless your going as Rapunzel or Jack Frost, you might want to consider incorporating a pair of shoes, slippers, or at 
            least socks, into your outfit!
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-sm-4 col-md-4">
        <h2>@Html.ActionLink("Bags", "Index", "Bags")</h2>
        <p>
            Sure you could put purses, bags, baskets, or fanny packs, into the accessories category, but since each cosplay can demand
            several accessories, why take up more room in that section than necessary?
        </p>
    </div>




    <div class="col-sm-4 col-md-4">
        <h2>@Html.ActionLink("Accessories", "Index", "Accessories")</h2>
        <p>
            Until further notice, anything you have left probably goes here!  Jewelry, crowns, wands, gloves, weapons, belts, and
            anything else not covered above!  -Be on the lookout for more available categories in the future!
        </p>
    </div>


</div>
